She looked at Megatron and glared.  He was laughing at her and she knew it.  
She looked at Terrorsaur and back at Megatron.
She walked back to her computer and sat down and tried not to look at either 
of the two bots.  She realy wanted Scorponok there right then.  But this 
time, she would have to fend for herself.
She looked at Megatron and said,
"Commander, if there is nothing else, I shall go to the lab and take care of 
thing."
She hoped Megatron would not command her to do anything and let her go to 
the lab without hassel.
